00:17:11.655 --> 00:17:15.079 align:middle line:90%


00:17:15.079 --> 00:17:19.109 align:middle line:84%
The dream of the planet
includes all of society's rules,

00:17:19.109 --> 00:17:21.694 align:middle line:84%
its beliefs, its
laws, its religions,

00:17:21.694 --> 00:17:24.750 align:middle line:84%
